{"id":306696,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/07/维权网-河南李玉凤-天津郑建慧邀请监察部进驻地/","date":"2013-07-31T17:03:17Z","modified":"2013-07-31T17:03:17Z","title":"维权网 | 河南李玉凤 天津郑建慧邀请监察部进驻地方“打苍蝇”反腐（图）","content":"<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员唐韵报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>日</span><span>，国家监察部门前拥满了上访维权的人们。在多年上访无果，问题得不到解决的情况下，到监察部门前控告。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>大批的保安、警察把守着监察部大门。警戒线拉起，访民维权不能越过半步。推搡中一名河南访民晕倒在马路上。河南焦作的李玉凤和天津的郑建慧也在监察部门前抗议司法腐败。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>她们针对“老虎、苍蝇一起打的口号”提出自己的看法：她们说：老虎是国家一级重点保护动物，国家也有立法，打老虎岂不是违反了《动物保护法》了吗？我们不能违法，不敢打”。而打苍蝇到是除四害，人人都该做，但百姓手里的苍蝇拍要是打腐败这个苍蝇却显得那么无能为力。所以希望监察部能够进驻到地方，倾听老百姓的声音，加大力度反腐败，而不仅只是流于形式上。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>河南李玉凤因拆迁案，《（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2000</span><span>）焦行监字第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>号》判决，胜诉后河南焦作法院及政府至今拆迁不予安置，错案不予赔偿。反而对李玉凤进行打击报复。多次非法拘禁、拘留，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2004</span><span>年以扰乱办公秩序的罪名把李玉凤劳动教养一年三个月，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2005</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">25</span><span>日</span><span>李玉凤去公安部反应“劳动教养问题行政复议，河南省公安厅长期不予答复”。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2007</span><span>年以李玉凤</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2005</span><span>年去公安部上访，并以“妨害公务罪”为由，判处李玉凤有期徒刑</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>年。身患三级胸水，继发性结核、肺癌等重病的李玉凤，监狱里受尽酷刑，被带手铐脚镣、倒背铐及</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>公斤</span><span>重镣。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>天津郑建慧</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13</span><span>岁的儿子</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1999</span><span>年因一起校园暴力导致一级伤残，法院鉴定造假，并在原告尹航“待诊”的情况下一次性结案，这起被告全责的案件，导致原告没有后期治疗费。《司法部司鉴中心</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">(2004)</span><span>精鉴字第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">272</span><span>好（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Q</span><span>）》鉴定，纠正了天津两个错误鉴定。郑建慧依照《民诉法》第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">179</span><span>条规定，以新的证据向最高法院申请再审。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2006</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">14</span><span>日</span><span>最高法院立案了。案件号《（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2006</span><span>）民一监字第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">462</span><span>号》和《（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2007</span><span>）民一监字第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">474</span><span>号》。但至今已经六年多了没给当事人审理结果。而最高法院却出了阴阳卷，即《（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2006</span><span>）民一监字第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">462-1</span><span>号》和《（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2007</span><span>）民一监字第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">474-1</span><span>号》。天津市第一中级法院的潘存杰是阴阳卷的造假者。现在郑建慧的儿子还在住院，却因欠医院巨额医疗费而得不到有效治疗。郑建慧表示一定依法为儿子维权到底。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<p></p>\n<div></div>\n<div></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-rM0A2Y_7D8A/UfjP9e6_r_I/AAAAAAAAmIM/nKwncU1aIUE/s1600/2013-07-30+.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-rM0A2Y_7D8A/UfjP9e6_r_I/AAAAAAAAmIM/nKwncU1aIUE/s320/2013-07-30+.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-0sGFWy_2S9c/UfjQAfFLQ6I/AAAAAAAAmIc/A8-nkojl7q4/s1600/2013-07-30+09.21.28.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-0sGFWy_2S9c/UfjQAfFLQ6I/AAAAAAAAmIc/A8-nkojl7q4/s1600/2013-07-30+09.21.28.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-V6wARnpvmaE/UfjP_m9COHI/AAAAAAAAmIY/j9IzN8J20ck/s1600/IMG00043.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"262\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-V6wARnpvmaE/UfjP_m9COHI/AAAAAAAAmIY/j9IzN8J20ck/s320/IMG00043.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div></div>\n<div></div>\n<p></p>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[19196]}